            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xE4DC5FBF<!--String: "Raheel, Toshie, and Nigel were all childhood friends. I mean, Nigel and Raheel not so much anymore, but all the same. Raheel is my brother and sure, we get along well, but I always felt like I was on the outside when we were little. Now I guess I really am on the outside—literally! I like having a sense of humor about these things."--></T>
                  <T>0xEE583E0E<!--String: "I know people say stuff like this to the point where it's a cliché, but the reason I love butterflies so much is because I like watching their growth stages and I like seeing them transform into something beautiful and unique. A lot of moths have a very short life once they've finally emerged from their cocoons. But I wonder what their sense of time is—maybe a few days is ages and ages to them."--></T>
                  <T>0xDC6B75F9<!--String: "One thing I really like about Sims coming here for their Getaways is that it gives me the opportunity to be social with more people. I can be shy, but I'm working on it a little every day."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
            <V n="title" t="enabled">
